contentrichtext.text: '''Ocuituco''' is a city in the [[Mexican state]] of [[Morelos]]. It stands at {{coord|18|52|N|98|46|W|}}. <!--- 18º52´3” N. and 98º 46´ W. ---> The city serves as the municipal seat for the surrounding municipality of the same name. The municipality reported 15,090 inhabitants in the year 2000 census. ==External links== *http://www.e-morelos.gob.mx/e-gobierno/DirMunicipios/ocuituco.htm *http://e-municipios.e-morelos.gob.mx/ocuituco.htm [[Category:Populated places in Morelos]] {{Morelos-geo-stub}} {{Morelos}}
